snippet.title: Amber Heard & Bots - Johnny vs Amber DiscoveryPlus
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard & Bots: "6000 fake or inauthentic accounts that were targeting Amber Heard." - says Chris Bouzy, CEO of Botsentinel to Discovery Plus UK.
- "Disinformation campaign... a coordinated influence campaign...you really didn't have to be a pro to see it... one of the most sophisticated online targeted attacks we'd seen."

BotSentinel started analysis in early 2020.
Context - 9,000 accounts in Azerbaijan operation on Facebook found by Sophie Zhang. 
Meaning: Johnny Depp hired Adam Waldman who worked for a Foreign Minister of Russia & Russian Oligarch, & JD recently met Serbia's leadership... he's using "dictator-level" disinformation operations. 

Q: Why do you think 6,000 accounts was never said prior and further analysis did not continue on their end?

#JohnnyDepp #Discovery #World #News
